# Experiment workspaces: ignore transient working files, but keep the durable
# record tracked — this .gitignore plus the ARC AnGels channel README.
# Note: a re-include cannot reach a file whose parent dir is excluded, so the
# directory must be re-included before the file (a leading "./" is invalid here).
*
!.gitignore
!agent-rapid-communication-and-gellings/
!agent-rapid-communication-and-gellings/README.md
